snippet.textDisplay: Ms World is something that we Filipinos don’t give much focus. Whoever wins the pageant, we’ll be happy. We have our own representative just for the reason to represent our nation. Expecting fr it is something we have let go & moved on a long time ago. To our representative, Michelle Dee, we wish for your best enjoyment to this journey. This is a once in a lifetime opportunity.  Win or lose , it doesn’t really matter at all. Just enjoy, have a good time bonding with your co candidates & that’s important. Have a safe journey back home, too..Congratulations to whoever is the winner!!👍🏻
